        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Heading",
            "content": [
                "In your slides text you can use [links](http://google.com) and various inline elements for _emotional_ and __strong__ emphasis or just for *italic* or **bold** decoration. `<code>` is used for inline code samples."
            ],
            "footer": "Presenter note for the second slide"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Two rows.>> Mighty heading",
            "content": [
                "You can use two lines header but it would reduce space on a slide. The 'Ribbon' theme is designed for seven lines of code after one-line header by default.",
                {
                    "footnote": "This paragraph could be used as a footnote"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Various lists",
            "content": [
                {
                    "bullets": [
                        "Simple lists are marked with bullets.",
                        "Ordered lists begin with a number.",
                        "You can even nest lists one inside another.",
                        {
                            "numlist": [
                                "Or mix their types.",
                                "But do not go too far.",
                                "Otherwise audience will be board."
                            ]
                        },
                        "Look, seven rows exactly!"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Serious Citation",
            "content": [
                {
                    "citation": {
                        "quote": "You can wrap one or more paragraphs into citation, which will make text italic and add a nice quote on the left. Giving the citation source would make it even more serious.",
                        "author": "Vadim Makeev"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "When you have a lot of code",
            "content": [
                {
                    "code": [
                        "<html lang=\"en\">",
                        {
                            "codeline": [
                                {
                                    "marked": "<head>"
                                },
                                " ",
                                {
                                    "marked": "<!--Comment-->",
                                    "codeclass": "comment"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "    <title>Shower</title>",
                        {
                            "codeline": [
                                "    <meta charset=\"",
                                {
                                    "marked": "UTF-8",
                                    "codeclass": "important"
                                },
                                "\">"
                            ]
                        },
                        "    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"s/screen.css\">",
                        "    <script src=\"j/jquery.js\"></script>",
                        {
                            "codeline": [
                                {
                                    "marked": "</head>"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Code in separate blocks",
            "content": [
                {
                    "code": [
                        {
                            "codeline": [
                                {
                                    "marked": "<html"
                                },
                                "lang=\"en\">"
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "footnote": "Now you can add a note for each block"
                },
                {
                    "code": [
                        {
                            "codeline": [
                                {
                                    "marked": "<meta"
                                },
                                " charset=\"",
                                {
                                    "marked": "UTF-8"
                                },
                                "\">"
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "footnote": "And explain what is interesting about it"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "title": "You can shout>> this way"
        },
